<!--index.wxml-->
<view class="container">
	<cover-image src="../images/index_38.jpg"> </cover-image>
	<view class="map_section">
		<cover-image class="map_icon" src="../images/map.png"> </cover-image>
		<picker bindchange="bindPickerChange" value="{{index}}" range="{{array}}">
			<view class="map_picker">
				{{array[index]}}
			</view>
		</picker>
	</view>
	<view class="order_info">
		<text class="order_info1">配餐说明</text>
		<text class="order_info2">1.目前仅支持北京美莱员工使用配餐预定功能</text>
		<text class="order_info2">2.每日10：00-13：00可预定当日午餐，14：30-18：30可预订当日晚餐。</text>
		<text class="order_info2">3.每日午/晚餐均可选择堂食或者打包（打包时无法选择菜品）。</text>
		<text class="order_info2">4.早餐需在8：45之前直接在食堂领取或堂食即可，无需预定。</text>
		<text class="order_info2">5.疫情期间特殊供餐，无法覆盖特殊饮食需求，请大家见谅。</text>
		<navigator url="/pages/order/order">
			<button class="order_btn">点击预定</button>
		</navigator>

		<view class="nav">
			<navigator url="/pages/order/order" open-type="redirect" hover-class="other-navigator-hover">我的预定</navigator>
			<navigator url="/pages/feedback/feedback">意见反馈</navigator>
			<navigator url="/pages/detaileddesc/detaileddesc">详细说明</navigator>

		</view>
	</view>
	<view class="userinfo">
		<cover-image src="../images/logo.jpg" class="logo"></cover-image>
		<text class="userinfo-nickname">{{userInfo.nickName}}</text>
	</view>
</view>